📍 Google My Business: RESTOSOFTIN 

🚀 About RestosoftIN
RestosoftIN is a powerful restaurant management software designed to streamline operations for restaurants, cloud kitchens, and cafés. Our software offers a seamless experience, from order management, billing, POS, inventory tracking, and customer engagement.

✅ Key Features
✔ POS System – Easy-to-use billing and invoicing system.
✔ Online Ordering – Integrate with Swiggy, Zomato, and WhatsApp.
✔ Kitchen Display System (KDS) – Track and manage orders efficiently.
✔ Inventory Management – Real-time stock tracking to reduce wastage.
✔ Customer Management – Loyalty programs, SMS, and WhatsApp notifications.
✔ Multi-Branch Support – Manage multiple outlets from a single dashboard.
✔ Mobile & Cloud Support – Access your restaurant data anytime, anywhere.
